Summary: Black disc moving at high rate of speed.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was out back filming for a Disc object that I have been seeing in the air. And out of no where a disc shape object shot across the sky above my head at a high rate of speed, made little to no sound, maybe a slight high pitch whistle hum, like a wind sound... Look Closely at 56 sec into the video, goes by very fast! Left then makes a quick bend to the right .
